**Savannah Informatics - Backend Engineer Assessment**

This project is a Django REST API for a simple e-commerce system, developed as part of the Savannah Informatics Backend Engineer technical assessment

**Features**

Customer, Product, and Order management

Hierarchical product categories of arbitrary depth

Authentication via OpenID Connect (OIDC)

REST API for all core functionalities

SMS notifications on order placement via Africaâ€™s Talking

Email alerts to admins on order placemen


**Tech Stack**

Backend: Python, Django, Django REST Framework

Database: PostgreSQL

Authentication: OIDC

Containerization: Docker

CI/CD: GitHub Actions

Deployment: Kubernetes


**API Endpoints**



**LOCAL SETUP**
git clone https://github.com/YOUR-USERNAME/savannah-backend-engineer-test.git
cd savannah-backend-engineer-test


**Create & activate virtualenv**
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate -->>ON MAC/LINUX MACHINES
       venv\Scripts\activate --> ON WINDOWS MACHINES ONLY







